# Walkthrough: Universal Project Modernization (Forest & Slate)

We have successfully completed a full-scale modernization of the **Bolsa de Proyectos SENA** platform. Every user role now interacts with a world-class, glassmorphic interface designed for clarity, efficiency, and professional appeal.

## 🌟 The "Forest & Slate" Design System
Our new visual language is built on:
- **Emerald Accents**: Symbolizing growth and the SENA identity.
- **Glassmorphism**: Soft background blurs and subtle borders for a premium feel.
- **Bento-Grid Layouts**: Organizing complex data into intuitive, digestible modules.
- **Responsive Fluidity**: Seamless experience across all devices.

